nt with Abram, saying, Unto thy seed have I given this land, from the river of Egypt unto the great river, the river Euphrates:","year":-1911},{"id":"rec1zfGamwrZNx99c","ref":"Gen.21.21","text":"And he dwelt in the wilderness of Paran: and his mother took him a wife out of the land of Egypt.","year":-1892}]}
